{{notability|prof|date=July 2016}} {{Underlinked|date=May 2014}}
'''Vergilius Ture Anselm Ferm''' (1896 &ndash; February 4, 1974 in [[Wooster, Ohio]]) was the Compton [[Professor]] of [[Philosophy]] at the [[College of Wooster]].
